              "id": "about-hero-text",
              "elType": "widget",
              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p style='color: #2C1810CC; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; margin: 0; font-weight: 300;'>With over two decades of experience crafting elevated interiors for discerning clients, I've built a practice rooted in timeless design principles, personal expression, and an unwavering commitment to beauty and function.</p><p style='color: #2C1810CC; font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; margin: 20px 0 0 0; font-weight: 300;'>Based in [CITY, STATE], my work has been featured in Architectural Digest, Elle Decor, House Beautiful, and Veranda, and recognized with multiple design awards.</p>",
                "typography_typography": "custom",
                "typography_font_size": {
                  "unit": "px",
                  "size": 18
                },
                "typography_font_size_tablet": {
                  "unit": "px",
                  "size": 16
